title: [Yegharren Valley, Wooded Slope]
description: Younger oaks and maples dot the hillside above an undergrowth of moonlit ferns and the dark forms of bushes.  The wind blows stronger here, occasional gusts from the east rustling ominously in the shadowy branches of the trees.

Younger oaks and maples dot the hillside above an undergrowth of bright ferns and berry bushes.  The wind blows stronger here, occasional gusts from the east rustling ominously in the branches of the trees.
